{"type":"message","id":"d85168dc","parentId":"ceda3152","timestamp":"2026-02-26T22:06:23.029Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Planning response for MV-SKILL**\n\nI need to acknowledge the user's request and offer to adjust the naming as needed. It seems like I should summarize the location and name MV-SKILL clearly. I should ask if they want any additional files or information. Additionally, I could mention next steps and possibly offer to add a static_scan.sh and findings template to enhance clarity. Overall, I’ll aim to keep everything concise, including the file path in my response.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] SKILLS.md created at:\n- /home/ec2-user/.openclaw/workspace/skills/malware-vet/SKILLS.md\n\nName: Malware Vetting Skill (MV-SKILL)\n\nSummary:\n- A repeatable, auditable workflow to inspect a ClawHub skill for malware before trusting or installing it.\n\nNext steps (optional):\n- I can add a minimal static_scan.sh script tailored to your environment.\n- I can add a ready-to-use Findings.md template to accompany reports.\n- Tell me which slugs you want initial vetting for (e.g., traffic-data, openclaw-safety-coach) and I’ll tailor the guide and include concrete commands."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":16150,"output":290,"cacheRead":4352,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20792,"cost":{"input":-16150,"output":-290,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":-16440}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772143577969}}
